---
<section class="problem">
  <div class="problem-wrap">
    <span class="reveal label">The Problem</span>
    <h2 class="reveal">Your website is <span class="serif">costing</span> you money</h2>
    <div class="problem-grid stagger">
      <div class="reveal problem-card">
        <div class="problem-num">4.2s</div>
        <h3>Slow load times</h3>
        <p>The average local business website takes 4+ seconds to load. Google says 53% of visitors leave if it takes longer than 3 seconds. That's half your traffic — gone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal problem-card">
        <div class="problem-num">72%</div>
        <h3>Not mobile-friendly</h3>
        <p>72% of consumers search for local businesses on their phone. If your site doesn't look and work perfectly on mobile, you're invisible to most of your potential customers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal problem-card">
        <div class="problem-num">#0</div>
        <h3>Invisible on Google</h3>
        <p>If you're not on page 1 for "nail salon near me" or "barber in [your city]," you don't exist. Most Wix and Squarespace sites can't compete on local SEO.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .problem{padding:100px 24px}.problem-wrap{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
  .problem h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:12px 0 48px}
  .problem-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px}@media(max-width:900px){.problem-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:480px}}
  .problem-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:32px 24px;transition:border-color 0.3s}.problem-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-lt)}
  .problem-num{font-size:40px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--pop);margin-bottom:12px}
  .problem-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}.problem-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
</style>
